Business Development Officer
Offshore Recruitment Services
UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Job Responsibilities:
•	Identify and increase potential customers and/or markets for sub franchising of the brands
•	Manage all sub franchising agreements, communication and other related matters
•	Develop, implement and execute company business plans and sales strategy
•	Identify market segments, growth opportunities, and evaluate competitive advantages, and communicate the requirements of these market segments to senior management.
•	Determine current and future needs by researching customer needs and wants and industry trends.
•	Represent the company and the brands at industry trade shows and conferences, as well as at customer presentations.
•	Understand and review P & L and other financial statements of the brands to have better understanding of the brand financial performance
•	Create, develop and maintain company newsletter for internal communication
•	Handles other sales and marketing activities as required by the line manager
REQUIREMENTS
Qualifications:
•	Bachelor’s Degree in Business Administration or related field
•	5 years’ experience in Sales, Business Development and Marketing, preferably in Food and Beverage industry
•	Fluent in English and Arabic
•	Proficiency in MS Office Applications
•	Willingness to travel as required
•	Excellent organization skills and ability to prioritize tasks
•	Strong presentation, sales and negotiation skills
•	Excellent customer service skills
Bachelor's Degree in Business Administration, Hospitality Management, Hotel Management
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
